about.summary: High level interface to SSPI for Kerberos client auth

name: winkerberos
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.7.0" %}

package:
  name: winkerberos
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/w/winkerberos/winkerberos-{{ version }}.zip
  sha256: e304c28de838a48206edfe58b8deb5209a3fd8c6a755bd521c1ee6e656b06e27

build:
  number: 1
  skip: True  # [not win or py27]
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - winkerberos

about:
  home: https://github.com/mongodb-labs/winkerberos
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "High level interface to SSPI for Kerberos client auth"
  license_family: Apache

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
